Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.10,0:02:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的消失了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 就说几句话也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.80,0:02:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经说了 我女儿不想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.30,0:02:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请通融一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧 不然就叫警察了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是柴田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.30,0:02:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要我等到什么时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片怎么样了啊 照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的 这礼拜一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 忘得一干二净了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是弘美小姐做的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.20,0:03:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这是我们店的主打产品 姐姐的得意之作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尝尝看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种触感是 腐竹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.90,0:03:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是弘美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个味儿可挺不好做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真是可惜这样的人才了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 还是希望你们能留在我们这一起做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 开店一直是姐姐和我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也是令尊的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 也请品尝一下这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.80,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个奶酪和豆腐的也很好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.80,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}甜蜜的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(400,120)\c&H51B748&\frz1}糕点坊『梦想』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(410,430)\c&H797979&\frz1}原创糕点品种齐全\N恭候各位光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄好了 弄好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.10,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 原来爸爸想象的厨房是这样的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 由香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.20,0:04:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这么快就把店开出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.50,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是托了每天打工一起攒钱的由香的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那是我该做的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我们两个决定的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是爸爸也能在这里做蛋糕就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过更重要的是今后的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.30,0:05:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须好好赚钱还债才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.70,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 有个好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 森崎先生那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他答应要是把姐姐的蛋糕带去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就帮忙在街角蛋糕节目中宣传咱们的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.70,0:06:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个节目很受欢迎的 正好能做宣传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拍摄是在下周六
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 由香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.80,0:06:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.30,0:06:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说要宣传当然是开张那天最好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好人啊 森崎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.50,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 当天把“遗产”拿出来不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.50,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}Héritage    法语【遗产】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她对姐姐的事赞不绝口呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻居们也深受其害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区政府也意识到要尽快处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在还没有有效的解决方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不是什么好照片啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要被总编骂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是街角蛋糕节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.50,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.60,0:07:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天首先由请森崎先生来介绍他的新作蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蛋糕叫什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字是“微醉”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}Ivresse      法语【微醉】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面用了神秘的材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能顺利进行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.90,0:07:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi 拍摄前一分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就照例叫出伊藤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.90,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 最喜欢甜食的记者伊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.40,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们采访的是本日开张的糕点坊『梦想』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位女糕点师是春日弘美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有她的妹妹由香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请她们马上介绍一下点心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.00,0:07:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.80,0:07:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我店的主打蛋糕“遗产”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蛋糕是姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本店的糕点师构思已久的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个跟刚才的蛋糕一样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}在原料中加入了切碎的腐竹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不是和森崎老师的一样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的 给我联系现场监督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是西式点心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吃起来就会有一种很亲切的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放广告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改成广告了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.50,0:08:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截稿了 截稿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和森崎先生的蛋糕一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.20,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我们没事先好好调查也有责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没想到会出来完全一样的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要模仿也无所谓啊 怎么偏偏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没模仿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.20,0:08:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.80,0:09:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳驾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收您两千圆 请稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你知道地狱通信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道知道 午夜零点登录的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以帮你消除怨恨的那个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工到太晚了 不快回去帮忙就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.20,0:09:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个店吧 最近剽窃森崎的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是原来的徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快会倒闭的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 估计是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天才有两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.10,0:10:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我还是想去找他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.90,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去了也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说还是别去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只是个传言吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.90,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.90,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已予受理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.00,0:12:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呼唤我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.90,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.50,0:12:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骗了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.50,0:12:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开店是死去的父亲 姐姐和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全家的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个梦想却被摧毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 请帮我消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨那个男人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨不得杀死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮入道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.00,0:13:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.80,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.30,0:13:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.90,0:13:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身也将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那是你死之后的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.00,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贷款到期了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也试着跟上面商量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.80,0:14:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 至少要是能还清利息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逾期的部分我们一定还清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.20,0:14:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请您再宽容一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜 我实在无能为力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以了吧 森崎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了 分店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.60,0:15:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店铺出租
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不去找那家伙的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.60,0:15:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是由香的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.80,0:15:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们会遇到这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又没做错什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.80,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些话和你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.10,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.30,0:16:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糕点品尝会    嘉宾 森崎伸也    赞助 目高电视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵店的事我听说了 很可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是你搞垮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是为了报复被姐姐甩掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厚颜无耻地亲近姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒绝了就做出这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么都随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在店也回不来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我很感谢你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.60,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你给了我绝好的复仇机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没想到会那么顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没这么痛快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.70,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就拼命工作还债吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.70,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我介绍你去个好地方怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.00,0:17:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都是相当漂亮的美人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.70,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.40,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 长衫放好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.40,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 各位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.50,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请品尝森崎先生的新品蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是森崎先生的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么蛋糕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么难吃也能吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们是白痴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们吃这种垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.20,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 住手 住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森崎伸也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.70,0:19:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那时电视上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个女孩在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 是做同一个蛋糕的女孩吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等 不是我 这蛋糕不是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.80,0:19:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说你的蛋糕是剽窃别人是真的咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是为了报复被女人甩掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是独家新闻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊 森崎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森崎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也对您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 尝尝我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪都行 快开车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.70,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是在做梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.00,0:20:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您喜欢吃甜食吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微尝到点教训了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们两人好不容易开的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己的所作所为道歉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.90,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉 为什么我要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.90,0:20:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真地喜欢她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直这么多关照她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她辜负了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么说呢 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.90,0:21:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.70,0:21:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.30,0:21:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那里 要去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.00,0:21:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的蛋糕再也不会给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.20,0:22:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森崎先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪都找不到啊
